MAIN RULES:

1. GIVE CREDIT
   If you use the code - just mention where you got it:
   "Original by pattmsc - https://pattmsc.online"

2. ABOUT COMMERCIAL USE
   This is a paid service with subscriptions (FREE, BASIC, PRO, ELITE).
   You can't:
   - Make your own paid service using this code
   - Sell subscriptions based on this project
   - Make money from it without permission
   - Remove the payment system

3. WHAT YOU CAN DO
   Commercial use only if:
   - You're integrating it into your own project (not a competitor)
   - Making internal company tools
   - Using for educational purposes

4. FORKS AND MODIFICATIONS
   - Fork and modify for yourself or learning - no problem
   - Just mention what you changed
   - Don't forget about the original author
   - Don't make it a paid service
   - If you publish a fork - link back to the original

5. FOR LEARNING AND PERSONAL USE
   For personal projects, learning, experiments - use as much as you want.

6. OFFICIAL SERVICE
   The only official paid service is here: https://pattmsc.online
   Want to launch your own commercial project - write to me.

7. CODE OWNERS & ANTI-PIRACY
   - Official code owners are defined in the .github/CODEOWNERS file of this
     repository.
   - Any commercial use, resale, hosting or integration of this project or
     substantial parts of its code into your own public or commercial project
     without explicit written permission from a code owner is prohibited.
   - You may not create or distribute builds, forks or services with identical
     or confusingly similar functionality that compete with the official
     service (https://pattmsc.online), whether paid or free.
   - Pirated, cracked or resold builds, keys or subscriptions are strictly
     forbidden.

